snippet.title: Axon TD: Uprising Announcement
snippet.description:
Axon TD is a Mazing Tower Defense where you can expand the map layout itself to your design. A huge arsenal of towers and a wide variety of enemies clash in a battleground that shifts on your whims. Engage in single or cooperative Tower Defense gameplay.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2296550/Axon_TD_Uprising__Tower_Defense

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/W7FWK8w
